      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0645P0-01462'>
        <a name='S5LV0645P0_20030226_GCR_83'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-wyn-roberts' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0645P0_20030226_GCR_83' title='Link to this speech by Mr Wyn Roberts' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-wyn-roberts" title="Mr Wyn Roberts">Lord Roberts of Conwy</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I am delighted to have had the chance to anticipate the best thoughts of the Assembly. I am glad that it has a limit of 15 in mind. That is an adequate number. In view of that assurance, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0645P0-01463'>
